---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Proxilyt"
  description="Privacy Policy for Proxilyt Local SEO Analytics"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100">
    <Header isHome={false} />

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-1 max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-16 sm:px-8 sm:py-20">
      <h1
        class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4"
        style="font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;"
      >
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-12">
        Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-gray-700">
        <p>
          At Proxilyt, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy
          Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your
          information when you visit our website and use our services.
          <br />
          By using our website and services, you consent to this policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          1. Information We Collect
        </h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>
            <strong>Information You Provide</strong>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Name</li>
              <li>Email address</li>
              <li>Business name</li>
              <li>Business category</li>
              <li>Business location</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Automatically Collected Information</strong>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>IP address</li>
              <li>Device information</li>
              <li>Browser type</li>
              <li>Usage Data</li>
              <li>Cookies</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Analytics & Infrastructure Providers</strong> we use:
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Supabase (data hosting)</li>
              <li>Cloudflare (security & performance)</li>
              <li>Google Analytics (traffic analytics)</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <br />
        <p>
          These providers may process data in accordance with their privacy
          policies.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          2. How We Use Your Information
        </h2>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Provide SEO analytics services</li>
          <li>Improve platform performance</li>
          <li>Send service-related emails</li>
          <li>Send marketing communications (you may unsubscribe anytime)</li>
          <li>Prevent fraud and abuse</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          3. Legal Basis (India Compliance)
        </h2>
        <p>We process personal data under:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Consent</li>
          <li>Contractual necessity</li>
          <li>Legitimate business interests</li>
          <li>
            Compliance with applicable Indian laws (Information Technology Act,
            2000)
          </li>
        </ul>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          4. Data Storage & Security
        </h2>
        <p>
          Your data is stored on Supabase infrastructure. We implement
          reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data.
          However, no system is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          5. Marketing Emails
        </h2>
        <p>We may send marketing emails about:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Feature updates</li>
          <li>New services</li>
          <li>Promotions</li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <p>You may unsubscribe at any time using the unsubscribe link.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          6. Data Sharing
        </h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share data only with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Infrastructure providers (Supabase, Cloudflare)</li>
          <li>Analytics providers (Google Analytics)</li>
          <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          7. Data Retention
        </h2>
        <p>We retain data as long as:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Your account remains active</li>
          <li>Required for legal compliance</li>
          <li>Necessary for legitimate business purposes</li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <p>You may request deletion by contacting us.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          8. Your Rights (India)
        </h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Correct inaccuracies</li>
          <li>Request deletion</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent</li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <p>
          To exercise rights: <a
            href="mailto:main.proxilyt@gmail.com"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">main.proxilyt@gmail.com</a
          >
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          9. Children's Privacy
        </h2>
        <p>
          Proxilyt is not intended for individuals under 18. We do not knowingly
          collect data from minors.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          10. International Expansion
        </h2>
        <p>
          If we expand outside India, additional compliance measures (such as
          GDPR) may apply.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          11. Changes to Privacy Policy
        </h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy periodically. Continued use constitutes
          acceptance.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">12. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Proxilyt</strong>
          <br />
          Panchkula, Haryana, India
          <br />
          <a
            href="mailto:main.proxilyt@gmail.com"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">main.proxilyt@gmail.com</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <Footer />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
